data.description: Beautiful large home for large family. This home consists of 4 bedrooms and 2 and half bathrooms plus the garage has been converted into an additional one bedroom one bathroom apartment! Home has a fully updated modern kitchen and updated bathrooms. Enjoy living in a great community close to the turnpike, while not having to deal with an association. Aside from having so much space and a great layout this home has a very large covered terrace to be able to enjoy hot summer days in the back. Home comes with an above ground pool, but you have plenty of space to build your dream pool as well. This home is ready for its next family!
